Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:45.23,Title,,0,0,240,,{\fad(800,800)}No Meu Caminho
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:47.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você me impede?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:56.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu só queria esmagar a cabeça do Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:04.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Colisão de Haoshoku Haki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele também possui isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha-ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:26.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,979)}Como eu imaginei, ele também...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.55,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O-O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.05,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:46.81,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Todos perderam a consciência?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:50.12,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Isso é Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.06,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Haki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:54.96,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,E Haoshoku Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.15,0:02:59.90,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,É a prova de que você tem \Nas qualidades de um rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:04.62,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:10.58,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você é o homem escolhido pelos céus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:17.00,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Agora...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:21.52,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Se você é um homem, deveria se testar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:25.93,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Tem alguém que você queira matar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:30.92,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)}Quer que eu te dê o poder para se vingar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.44,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Tem um monte de caras...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.66,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...que eu quero matar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:54.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Doffy é diferente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Completamente diferente!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Seu nascimento o levou à loucura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Seu destino alimentou sua raiva!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:06.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,538)}Isso o transformou em um verdadeiro demônio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:13.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele realmente se tornou o mal definitivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:20.99,Main,,0,0,0,,E daí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:43.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Vá para o inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.59,Main,,0,0,0,,A loucura de Doffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:24.67,Main,,0,0,0,,...vai destruir tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.14,Main,,0,0,0,,...Eagle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.48,Main,,0,0,0,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Athlete!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Beta Betton!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.53,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Não pense que um fracote \Ncomo você pode derrotar Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, Doffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou parar o Chapéu de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:51.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Esmague a cabeça do Law agora que você pode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso, Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Lute comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Tral não consegue se mover nem um milímetro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu disse: "Espere sua vez"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Seu maldito pegajoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sou grudento!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.67,Main,,0,0,0,,É inútil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.70,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:25.91,Main,,0,0,0,,O que isso significa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Com o meu Busoshoku Haki, \Neu deveria conseguir acertar os Logia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:33.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, será que meu poder é do tipo Logia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:38.29,Main,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, isso não vai funcionar comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiota de borracha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele está certo, é inútil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Contra aquele bastardo de papel machê!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:53.95,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Papel machê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:58.98,Main,,0,0,0,,O principal motivo pelo qual eu não queria sentar no Trono de Copas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,era porque eu não queria ser colocado junto com idiotas como eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que você ainda consegue falar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,O que diabos você está dizendo, seu maldito moribundo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.29,0:08:14.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Nós, oficiais supremos, somos \Nas pedras angulares da família!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:18.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou perdoar quem zombar de nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Beta Betton...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.79,Main,,0,0,0,,...Launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Tral já não consegue se mover!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:32.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Law, desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou dar uma lição nesse moleque!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:38.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Sai da frente, Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouça, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:47.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Doffy sempre será o rei absoluto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:55.22,Main,,0,0,0,,...não há diferença entre ele e \Nseus atuais oficiais supremos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.80,Main,,0,0,0,,E isso é porque...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:09:00.85,Main,,0,0,0,,...cerca de trinta anos atrás...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:07.19,Main,,0,0,0,,...nós quatro pegamos esse \Ntalento ilimitado que caiu do céu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:14.57,Main,,0,0,0,,demos poder a ele e o criamos \Npara ser o ícone do mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.68,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Quase te mataram na \NTerra Sagrada de Mariejoa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:24.50,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Mesmo depois de levar a cabeça do seu pai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:32.74,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Mas estou feliz que você voltou vivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.74,0:09:35.04,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,É um milagre!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:44.77,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Doffy, você tem as qualidades de um rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:51.82,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Doffy, faremos tudo o que você disser.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:59.07,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Doffy, em troca, mostre-nos seu sonho!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.37,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O que houve, Doffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.84,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,E essa ferida?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.32,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Um bandido fez isso comigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.18,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Esse cara deveria morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:19.74,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:20.96,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.56,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O que diabos você quer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:38.21,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, foi você \Nquem machucou o Doffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.16,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ah, aquele moleque.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.70,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Só dei uma assustada nele!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.28,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:47.41,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Alguém te machucou de novo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.79,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não, eu caí porque a \Nestrada estava em mau estado.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.98,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,A estrada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.34,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Em que cidade foi isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.52,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:59.20,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Precisamos consertar isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:23.31,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ouça, Doffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:26.27,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você é um rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:29.75,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ninguém deve se rebelar contra você.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:35.63,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Você é o homem que um dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:40.55,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...se tornará o rei dos mares!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:56.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Preparamos Doffy como um rei e \Nnossos subordinados conheceram a dignidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:12:02.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas, da mesma forma, nós cinco, incluindo Doffy, nos tratamos como iguais na família!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,E chegamos até aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Como uma família!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:11.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Entende, Law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Lembra que meu muco é inflamável?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:22.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Em um instante, sua boca insolente...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.81,0:12:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma família?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:29.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Só vocês pensam assim, Trébol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Vocês não significam nada para ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você disse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Que patético.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Para mim, até você, que age \Ncomo se fosse o chefe de pessoal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:50.32,Main,,0,0,0,,não passa de uma marionete estúpida \Nde Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:55.37,Main,,0,0,0,,M-Marionete estúpida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou te perdoar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Não caia no jogo dele, Trébol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:04.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está dentro do Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:08.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu parei os movimentos \Ndesse moleque moribundo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.38,Main,,0,0,0,,...com meu muco!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:13.18,Main,,0,0,0,,O que ele pode fazer nessa condição?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, abra a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:22.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Moleque insolente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou atravessar sua garganta com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu também sou capitão de um navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:40.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Se eu deixar o Chapéu de Palha-ya \Ncuidar de você e de Doflamingo,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.42,Main,,0,0,0,,perderei minha honra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Você nem consegue se mover!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.04,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você pode fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito verme!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Morra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Tact!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas o quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.30,Main,,0,0,0,,O braço?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Sterben!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:19.71,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1116,42)\fs22}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(250,250)}QUARTO NÍVEL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:19.71,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1110,455)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(250,250)}CAMPO\N DE GIRASSÓIS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Aconteceu algo, Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:28.53,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(532,0)}FÁBRICA DE SMILE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.02,Main,,0,0,0,,O que foi, pessoal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:35.12,Main,,0,0,0,,De repente, todos olharam para a cidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:39.92,Main,,0,0,0,,N-Não sei por que, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:44.36,Main,,0,0,0,,...me sinto aliviado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, não temos tempo para isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Já terminamos de destruir a fábrica!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora temos que fugir dessa jaula que está se aproximando!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.63,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1125,405)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(350,350)}PALÁCIO REAL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:15.18,Main,,0,0,0,,O que diabos é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Um cara magro saiu do viscoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Então foi por isso que não consegui acertá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:50.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja, Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Que idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Você também vai morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:15.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele quer se incendiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:19.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou te levar comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:36.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma enorme chama saiu do Palácio Real!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.84,0:16:40.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffyland!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.51,0:16:46.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele vai ficar bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos que ajudá-lo de alguma forma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:48.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:48.73,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se envolvam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Na verdade, vocês só atrapalhariam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:54.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Até Trafalgar Law, que é membro dos Shichibukai, assim como Doflamingo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.50,Main,,0,0,0,,foram gravemente feridos!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:04.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Lawland!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:05.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:07.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Jogue o Tral-kun para mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:09.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:10.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:11.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixo ele com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Tral já lutou o suficiente contra Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:16.92,Main,,0,0,0,,O braço dele...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Cem Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Spider Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.32,Main,,0,0,0,,O braço de Lawland...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Que crueldade...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:43.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tral-kun, aguente firme!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Não faça nada desnecessário!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele ainda está respirando.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele não pode ir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Esse maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:17:58.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele ainda está perseguindo Tral!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:17:59.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Este é o golpe final!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:04.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Tamaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,...Hawk Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:14.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Robiland!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Tral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:19.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:26.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Machado de Metal Precioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:30.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Cabbage-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu estive dormindo até agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:38.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Você ainda não terminou \Nisso, Chapéu de Palha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.24,0:18:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:46.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Leve os outros para baixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Não diga bobagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:50.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Já que tenho Doflamingo à vista,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:53.11,Main,,0,0,0,,eu também quero dar um golpe nele!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.14,0:18:56.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Conto com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Con...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Conta comigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:03.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Confiança...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:07.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Popularidade...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Idolatria!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha é meu fã.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Um pedido de um fã...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:24.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Não posso recusar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:27.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Bartolomeo deve estar no nível inferior!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:30.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos usar a habilidade dele para descer daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Há algo que você possa fazer, Leo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:42.82,Main,,0,0,0,,A ferida está em mau estado!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:45.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Se eu conseguir costurar bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:47.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você conseguir,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.42,Main,,0,0,0,,poderei curá-lo com meu regador.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.88,Main,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, vamos fazer \No que Lucy disse e descer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Bartolomeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Faça escadas com sua habilidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Zoro-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Para sempre!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:10.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está me ouvindo, desgraçado?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Já chega,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:36.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Tral está sofrendo por não poder morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Precisamos deixá-lo descansar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:43.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Se é isso que você quer fazer, \Nterá que me derrotar primeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:51.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que você já está \Nbem enfraquecido.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Você também!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:58.32,Main,,0,0,0,,É impossível que todos esses \Nataques de Tral não tenham te afetado!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é rápido mesmo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:30.64,Main,,0,0,0,,mas falta peso a você.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:32.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Superaquecimento!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:40.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Que nostálgico!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:45.06,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Crocodile foi derrotado?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:49.12,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Por um capitão do Quartel-General da Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.88,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não minta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.88,0:21:52.32,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Deve haver algo por trás disso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:54.68,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Olhe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.04,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Foi esse cara!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.08,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Sua recompensa aumentou de repente!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:01.34,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Investiguem essa tripulação.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:02.71,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não a conheço.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.64,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Monkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.64,0:22:07.22,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,738)}D?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:12.51,Main,,0,0,0,,E na Grande Guerra você caiu do céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que você sobreviveu \Ne chegou até aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.87,0:22:43.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:47.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Você recuperou a consciência, Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:51.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Me deixe aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.36,0:22:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você está dizendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Durante treze anos,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:04.90,Main,,0,0,0,,eu só vivi para derrotar Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:22.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Já fiz tudo o que pude!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:29.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tenho outra opção a não ser confiar \No resto ao Chapéu de Palha-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:35.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Se ele vencer,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:37.77,Main,,0,0,0,,quero ver com meus próprios olhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:49.99,Main,,0,0,0,,E se ele perder, preciso ficar aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:53.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...para morrer junto com ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.23,0:24:19.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:23.40,Main,,0,0,0,,...coloquei ele nessa luta...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.23,0:24:30.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Quero ver daqui com meus próprios olhos!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.20,0:24:32.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Me deixe aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Trafalgar...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.37,0:24:37.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Tral-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.91,0:24:41.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Supõe-se que capitães aliados \Nestejam na mesma posição.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.26,0:24:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.34,0:24:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,...está aqui por sua própria vontade.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.64,0:24:50.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele não lutaria se não fosse \Nsua vontade fazê-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.76,0:24:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Me deixe aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.01,0:24:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu te imploro!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.61,0:25:10.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que não vou te convencer...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.44,0:25:13.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Nico Robin, vá na frente.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.98,0:25:17.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Cabbage-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.68,0:25:22.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou ouvir seus desejos suicidas.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.76,0:25:24.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Também vou ficar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.66,0:25:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas se comprometa.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.96,0:25:30.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você morrer,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.14,0:25:32.92,Main,,0,0,0,,será depois de mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.26,0:25:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.34,0:25:38.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Robin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.39,0:25:41.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Bartolomeo fez escadas para nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.99,0:25:42.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Vá.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.14,0:25:46.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Vá, use isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.24,0:25:52.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Gear Third!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.80,0:25:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.20,0:26:02.16,Main,,0,0,0,,...Grizzly Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.54,0:26:07.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está cheio de pontos fracos!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.86,0:26:24.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não quer que o ataque de Law seja em vão?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.52,0:26:29.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando você vai...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.34,0:26:31.82,Main,,0,0,0,,...me derrotar?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.82,0:26:35.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Você tem um limite de uma hora.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.61,0:26:39.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Nesse tempo, a jaula se fechará completamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.74,0:26:47.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Com certeza há pessoas com \Nproblemas nas pernas.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.68,0:26:51.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Também há pessoas acamadas, \Nidosos e bebês.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.48,0:26:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem será a primeira vítima?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.72,0:27:04.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Em trinta minutos, \Ncomeçarão a haver mortes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.43,0:27:10.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Após quarenta minutos, poderemos \Nouvir os gritos daqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.60,0:27:12.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Em cinquenta minutos,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.90,0:27:18.53,Main,,0,0,0,,o país estará tingido de vermelho, \Ncomo se você tivesse esmagado tomates.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.62,0:27:29.00,Main,,0,0,0,,E quando a hora se cumprir, \Nnão se ouvirá mais nenhuma voz.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.98,0:27:36.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Provavelmente você não se importa \Ncom o que acontece com Dressrosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.58,0:27:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,mas aqueles que estão prestes a morrer odiarão vocês.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.89,0:27:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Se vocês não tivessem vindo, ainda haveria paz em Dressrosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.22,0:27:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Mentiroso!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.94,0:27:51.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Era só por fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.52,0:28:05.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Há pessoas com má sorte por toda parte!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.74,0:28:08.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Você nunca conseguirá salvar todos.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.00,0:28:11.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Você é só um pirata de passagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.22,0:28:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Está tentando bancar o herói?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.12,0:28:16.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Como se atreve a se meter no meu caminho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.67,0:28:18.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Você está errado!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.08,0:28:20.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Você se meteu no meu caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.97,0:28:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Você fez meus amigos chorarem...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.78,0:28:26.80,Main,,0,0,0,,...e deixou meus companheiros furiosos!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.89,0:28:34.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas, como você ainda não caiu,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.81,0:28:37.07,Main,,0,0,0,,eu assumirei a responsabilidade por tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.07,0:28:39.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Não vou deixar ninguém morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.16,0:28:47.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Você e a jaula estão no meu caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.96,0:28:52.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Gear...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.57,0:28:55.60,Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição:\N Galaxy 9000\N\NTempos:\N Datenshi\NSewil (Opening)\NUmim\N\NControle de qualidade:\N Feeso\NGalaxy 9000\NMr. Luffy\NGrug\NDatenshi\NFJATP\N\NMestre musical:\N Halee\N\NCartazes:\N Datenshi\N\NTradução: Juan Tlgd\NRevisão: RAFAEL
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.54,0:28:55.60,Main,,0,0,0,,...Fourth!
